text: Highly recommend dropping by if you’re in the vicinity. A Most Absurd Guide is very well put together if you’re into modern work with a twist of humor.
Very friendly folks and interesting exhibits with affordable art pieces
Local art scene represent! If you’re in the area it’s a must to drop by to see what local artists are cooking up.
They sell products that they do not have with no communication or refunds.
Friendly people with the know-how in the current advertising and marketing climate. Supportive of the creative industry and has their own gallery showcasing local/International exhibitions
